Default iconv on solaris is unusable.

Instead please install the GNU iconv and we will arrange MarpaX::ESLIF to link/compile with it.
On my box (openindiana) this was achieved with:

# pkg install libiconv

Note the installation directories for include and libraries with:

# pkg contents libiconv

